    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A NEW UNDERGRÔUND STAGE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ô</strong> is a new kind of musical game centered on techno. We're collaborating directly with artists and labels to bring their music to life. Experience the sound in your own way and reach the best score before the end of the mix.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GROOVE TO FIND THE MOVE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199890/extras/48cabe6531bba43c5a49ad8c26e005ae.poster.avif?t=1757495233\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199890/extras/48cabe6531bba43c5a49ad8c26e005ae.webm?t=1757495233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199890/extras/48cabe6531bba43c5a49ad8c26e005ae.mp4?t=1757495233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dance with any instrument of the tracks in each level. Compose your own choreography based on bass, drums, melodies or lyrics. You'll encounter other enemy dancers with their own moveset. Move as close to them at the right timing to electrocute the closest ones, flirt with them ! It's a french game after all...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But not too close, you'll get hurt and it will ruin the show.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GEAR UP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199890/extras/b9cd1418543368709b9c8c20e8b294e8.poster.avif?t=1757495233\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199890/extras/b9cd1418543368709b9c8c20e8b294e8.webm?t=1757495233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199890/extras/b9cd1418543368709b9c8c20e8b294e8.mp4?t=1757495233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock upgrades, customize automated weapons activated by the sounds of the music. You'll earn resources along the way that you can spend to come up with the best strategy. Find out which weapon works best with each kind of sound you hear.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> &quot;This bass had massive volume and long sustained notes...I can slide to it.&quot;</i></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;This automated weapon works best connected to this gatling gun drum beat !&quot;</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;If I stack this passive upgrade, it will boost the voice track's power.&quot;</i></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DIG THE MAP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199890/extras/fbcfbc1fc120218f5ae41a1e8eb0ed42.poster.avif?t=1757495233\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199890/extras/fbcfbc1fc120218f5ae41a1e8eb0ed42.webm?t=1757495233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199890/extras/fbcfbc1fc120218f5ae41a1e8eb0ed42.mp4?t=1757495233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the procedurally generated map. In it, you'll encounter fights, time trials or several recurrent rooms filled with all kinds of upgrades. The map generation can be customized in many ways to make sure it adapts to your needs and strategy. Better get moving though ! Time is ticking and the end of the song is coming.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PRICK UP YOUR EAR</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199890/extras/aad46aeda243b39418f99dafb07112f2.poster.avif?t=1757495233\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199890/extras/aad46aeda243b39418f99dafb07112f2.webm?t=1757495233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199890/extras/aad46aeda243b39418f99dafb07112f2.mp4?t=1757495233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pay close attention to the music, events will occur as it progresses. Get ready for a boss fight on the drop. Take advantadge of respites to spend your resources and rethink your strategy. Soon enough, you'll read music instinctively and vibe with all of its variations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
